

   (1)   SQL
         +  Using SQL (or) HiveQL Queries
   (2)   DataFrames
         +  Similar to table in RDBMS
         +  Can be constructed from 
            -  Hive
            -  External Databases
            -  Existing RDDs
   (3)   Datasets
         +  Constructed from
            -  JVM Objects
         +  Provides much better optimization over DataFrames  #2          
                           
